      • MACRO_LOT49_IMPRESSION

        static final String MACRO_LOT49_IMPRESSION
        Is substituted with the URL to Lot49 impression handler. It will automatically include the appropriate exchange's winning price macro.

      • MACRO_LOT49_CLICK

        static final String MACRO_LOT49_CLICK
        Is substituted with the URL to Lot49 click handler. The appropriate exchange-specific macro is automatically included and placed in the right place in the expanded URL unless it is explicitly specified elsewhere in the tag template.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • MACRO_LOT49_EXCHANGE_CLICK_ENC

        static final String MACRO_LOT49_EXCHANGE_CLICK_ENC
        Is substituted with the appropriate encoded click macro from the exchange.

        If present in the tag template, any of the instances of MACRO_LOT49_CLICK/ MACRO_LOT49_CLICK_ENC will not automatically include this.
